    <item>
      <title>拉加德（Lagarde）看到AI可能在欧洲繁殖不平等的危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/lagarde-sees-danger-that-ai-could-breed-inequality-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲中央银行总裁克里斯汀·拉加德（Christine Lagarde）表示，如果各国不培养利用这种技术的技能，人工智能可能会破坏该地区的社会模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/lagarde-sees-danger-that-ai-could-breed-inequality-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 13:03:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Starmer对父母在法庭上提出质疑的私立学校税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/starmer-s-tax-on-private-schools-challenged-in-court-by-parents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）征服私立学校的税收被描述为前所未有的镇压，违反了该国的人权义务，这是对该计划的第一个实质性法院挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/starmer-s-tax-on-private-schools-challenged-in-court-by-parents</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 13:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国卫生机构开始大规模裁员，因为RFK Jr.订购10,000个工作岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-health-agency-mass-firings-begin-as-kennedy-orders-10-000-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博社报道的一份备忘录，美国卫生和公共服务部开始于周二清晨解雇工人，包括涉及毒品和烟草安全的最高监管机构，因为秘书罗伯特·肯尼迪（Robert F. Kennedy Jr.]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-health-agency-mass-firings-begin-as-kennedy-orders-10-000-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 12:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
